These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-1::.
7 different games are played: bridge, billiard, snooker, poker, scrabble, canasta, whist
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, board-games, card-games, cooking, gardening, hiking, writing
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person playing billiard##1
 2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
 4. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person playing billiard##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
10. the person playing scrabble is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
13. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
14. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
15. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
16. the person playing poker is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
17. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
18. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |     6     |      7      |
| Game    | whist    | scrabble  | canasta       | billiard | bridge | snooker | poker        |
| Hobby   | gardening | hiking | card-games | baking    | writing   | cooking   | board-games |

