.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, mirinda, tea, water
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, backgammon, domino, poker, go, monopoly
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 3. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
 4. the person drinking water is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 6. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
10. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing go##1
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
15. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing billiard##1
16. the person playing billiard is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
17. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |      2      |    3    |    4    |       5       |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | fanta    | almond-milk | tea     | mirinda | hot-chocolate | water     | iced-tea |
| Game       | monopoly | go      | backgammon | poker  | billiard      | mah-jongg | domino   |

