.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, skydiving, writing
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, january, february, december, april, august, may
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
10. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
12. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
13. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
14. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
15. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |       3       |     4     |      5       |      6      |    7    |
