 9. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
10. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
11. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
12. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
13. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
14. the person driving the ship is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
